    "description": "<strong>我们总是在清醒的时候寻找真相，但是真相可能隐藏在我们的噩梦中…</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145220/extras/96dad665b497e0f767381f2f92be73cf.avif?t=1758833458\" width=602 height=204 /></span><br>被奇怪的声音惊醒，我睁开了眼睛。我坐在床上，惊魂未定，盯着那扇半开的门。门外有人用异样的眼神看着我，<br>门突然关上了！我清醒过来，意识到有人偷偷溜进了我家。那一刻我唯一能想到的就是报警，如果一切正常的话。<br>我要自己尝试走出这个迷宫，还是有人会帮助我？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145220/extras/17be985d16ddceb1324f56f013e438f8.poster.avif?t=1758833458\" width=602 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145220/extras/17be985d16ddceb1324f56f013e438f8.webm?t=1758833458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145220/extras/17be985d16ddceb1324f56f013e438f8.mp4?t=1758833458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Silence Channel”是一系列基于真实故事的心理恐怖游戏，每个篇章都有其独特的故事和角色剧情发展。在《Silence Channel 2》中，<br>玩家需要解开谜题，躲开敌人，找到隐藏的道具，甚至和奇怪的生物战斗，以揭露故事真相并逃出困境。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145220/extras/e908a004dec8928b8796d8f2fff84408.poster.avif?t=1758833458\" width=602 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145220/extras/e908a004dec8928b8796d8f2fff84408.webm?t=1758833458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145220/extras/e908a004dec8928b8796d8f2fff84408.mp4?t=1758833458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>本篇的故事也是基于真实故事改编的。在游戏的一开始，我们遇到了一个未知的角色，她在家中目睹了奇怪和超自然的事件，并竭尽全力逃离。<br>然后我们听到一名女士报警说有人闯入了她家，她需要帮助。这时，离房子最近的巡警·马丁<br>被派去调查现场，新的故事就此开始。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145220/extras/da76915eb90f700284ea99f9042e510f.poster.avif?t=1758833458\" width=602 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145220/extras/da76915eb90f700284ea99f9042e510f.webm?t=1758833458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145220/extras/da76915eb90f700284ea99f9042e510f.mp4?t=1758833458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>你可以在Instagram和X上关注我们以获取更多细节 (@LexipGames​)<br><br>游戏特色：<br>• 试图找到出路<br>• 穿过陌生而黑暗的地方<br>• 发现游戏背后的故事<br>• 生成的事件<br>• 随机元素<br>• 逼真的画面<br>• 各式各样的谜题<br>• 躲藏和潜行",
